debrief:
Thank you for participating in our study! This is a pilot study for a project on people's usage of AI for generating creative ideas. We are interested in exploring the creativity of people's ideas when they use vs. do not use AI. Out of those who were assigned to use AI, we varied whether they received guidance to stay in control of the tool or let the tool control them. This project may help determine whether people's psychological approaches to AI-based tools bears on their actual and perceived creativity.

Below, you can optionally provide feedback about the study. Did you run into any technical issues? Was anything confusing?
